text: i love the place, so accessible and comfortable

Highly unprofessional staff at Jurong! Invited me and my kid for a hip hop dance trial class and when we reached Hougang center, we were told that they don't conduct hip hop dance classes there. Ruined our day.

For  Ballet for young kids, I strongly recommend Ms Shyamala.  She is able to control the class in a friendly and effective manner.  Most importantly, she is able to impart ballet effectively in a fun manner that keeps the child interested.
I Dance there it's awesome, Recomended teacher would be Ms Shyamala . Plus this dance school is right above NTUC . Walk a bit and you would reach Kovan Heartland mall! Also close to Kovan MRT!
